{"tid":1692666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益)新抗爭方法討論「#teamtrees計畫」","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:21:16.000Z","uid":131767,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b518748526f10d73884dfef61ebeec0d548dda7a","tid":1692666,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:44:13.000Z","msg":"首先我唔係反對現有嘅抗爭方法<br />\n只係想拋磚引玉brainstorm下<br />\n希望好似抗爭初期咁<br />\n以各種有創意嘅手段帶番起大家嘅熱情<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎批評，但係批評後請加埋你嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n#teamtrees計畫<br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://www.teamtrees.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teamtrees.org%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfr9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=4175844a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.teamtrees.org/</a><br />\nTeamTrees 計畫是由 MrBeast 的兩千萬訂閱企劃首先發起的，聯合各種Youtube創作者一起攜手創作各種&quot;種樹救地球&quot;的影片，企劃的目標是在2020種植&quot;20,000,000棵樹&quot;。MrBeast 與 Arbor Day Foundation(植樹節基金會)合作，每一塊美金就種植一棵樹，並確保每棵樹可以茁壯生長。現在，不只MrBeast，每個人都能參與這龐大的植樹計畫，<a href=\"http://只要到teamtrees.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AA%E8%A6%81%E5%88%B0teamtrees.org&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfr9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=def277d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">只要到teamtrees.org</a>的官方網站捐贈1$，就能種植一棵樹拯救地球。<br />\n已參與名人:<br />\nElon Musk (Tesla)<br />\nTobi Lutke (Shopify)<br />\nSusan Wojcicki (Youtube)<br />\nJack Dorsey (Twitter)<br />\nAlan Walker (DJ)<br />\nPewdiepie (Youtuber)<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;snA=5386634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60076%26snA%3D5386634&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfr9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=2d2449ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;snA=5386634</a><br />\n<br />\n行動建議:<br />\n由知名、有公信力youtuber發起眾籌<br />\n以香港示威者名義捐款<br />\n喺訊息欄填上支持香港訊息(eg fight for freedom, stand with hong kong<br />\n<br />\n行動方向參考:<br />\n大J 發起眾籌 援助日本重建<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654151</a><br />\n<br />\n可能有人話「點解唔幫手足先啊，好多手足飯都無錢食」<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">兩件事係完全無衝突</span></span><br />\n手足有難當然幫手足先<br />\n如果大家幫完仲有餘力<br />\n不失為一次新國際宣傳活動<br />\n<br />\n附上好耐無見過嘅口號<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後就算呢個行動俾大家ban咗<br />\n都希望激發到大家諗啲新嘅抗爭方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21ef92a3aead311d48ecab6166a0b8f7c3a92f5","tid":1692666,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"9f2938deb3e75cf0a3cddc5d48a49467f2672a0b","tid":1692666,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:45:52.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"7410da8d1850d089e40ccd67cffe720948ef7681","tid":1692666,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"有撚用"},{"pid":"5a21ec0df305bbd04104e5ecb00804b221179275","tid":1692666,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7410da8d1850d089e40ccd67cffe720948ef7681","tid":1692666,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"有撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅回覆<br />\n獲益良多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b451db4d124bf7eb9618ea1246c41a1cd533562b","tid":1692666,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"83790dcef10886130f840bba42c1a2b802f19da3","tid":1692666,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"37d4d21e0e